		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">42.1501</ph> General.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2547e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2561e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Past performance information (including the ratings and supporting narratives) is relevant information, for future source selection purposes, regarding a contractor’s actions under previously awarded contracts or orders. It includes, for example, the contractor’s record of-</p>
					          <ol id="d2547e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2561e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Conforming to requirements and to standards of good workmanship;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2561e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Forecasting and controlling costs;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2561e45" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Adherence to schedules, including the administrative aspects of performance;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2561e54" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Reasonable and cooperative behavior and commitment to customer satisfaction;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2561e63" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Reporting into databases (see subpart <xref href="FAR-i1121746.dita#i1121746"
                              base="i1121746"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">4.14</xref>, and reporting requirements in the solicitation provisions and clauses referenced in <xref href="FAR-i1116212.dita#i1116212"
                              base="i1116212"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">9.104-7</xref>);</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2561e79" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(6)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Integrity and business ethics; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2561e88" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(7)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Business-like concern for the interest of the customer.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2561e99" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Agencies shall monitor their compliance with the past performance evaluation requirements (see <xref href="FAR-i42_1502.dita#i42_1502"
                        base="i1074248"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42.1502</xref>), and use the Contractor Performance Assessment Reporting System (CPARS) and Past Performance Information Retrieval System (PPIRS) metric tools to measure the quality and timely reporting of past performance information.</p>
				        </li>
